OL,3,CDouglas Ross: I know I'm not
OL,4,Ceveryone's cup of tea
OL,6,FAfter facing down three first
OL,7,Fministers at Holyrood, Douglas Ross
OL,8,Fwill soon leave the Scottish
OL,9,FParliament.
OL,11,FRejected by voters in the general
OL,12,Felection last summer, the former
OL,13,FScottish Tory leader is undeterred and
OL,14,Fwill try his luck again at Westminster
OL,15,Fin 2029, unless an election is called
OL,16,Fsooner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
