CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1771830269
OL,3,CDouglas Ross: I know I'm not
OL,4,Ceveryone's cup of tea
OL,6,FThey were "probably glad to see the
OL,7,Fback of me", the Highlands and Islands
OL,8,FMSP added.
OL,10,FAs Scottish Conservative leader, he
OL,11,Fquestioned three first ministers:
OL,12,FNicola Sturgeon, Humza Yousaf and John
OL,13,FSwinney.
OL,15,FAll of them, he said, had "fiercely
OL,16,Fdifferent styles" but were united in
OL,17,F"assuming the SNP can do no wrong".
OL,19,F"I didn't have a good relationship
OL,20,Fwith any of them," Mr Ross said.
OL,26,@nD@KOUoD@KO]wD@[OUxD@QO]yD@AOUyD@bO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1771830269
OL,3,CDouglas Ross: I know I'm not
OL,4,Ceveryone's cup of tea
OL,6,F"And for me I'm quite happy with that.
OL,8,F"Nicola Sturgeon and I had no personal
OL,9,Frelationship at all.
OL,11,F"She would speak to (Scottish Labour
OL,12,Fleader) Anas (Sarwar) and (Scottish
OL,13,FLiberal Democrats leader) Alex Cole-
OL,14,FHamilton when we were grouped together
OL,15,Fas leaders.
OL,17,F"She didn't speak to me and I didn't
OL,18,Fspeak to her and I was quite happy
OL,19,Fabout that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
